Icon attribution
================

The three glyph icons bundled as GResources and drawn next to results are
copied verbatim from this repository's own Quickshell icon set:

    data/icons/search.svg
        <- config/quickshell/icons/search.svg
    data/icons/calculator.svg
        <- config/quickshell/icons/calculator.svg
    data/icons/web.svg
        <- config/quickshell/icons/web.svg

They are reused so the GTK launcher renders the same glyphs as the Quickshell
launcher it ports.

The application icons are original to this project:

    data/dev.sandip.Launcher.svg            (color, scalable/apps)
    data/dev.sandip.Launcher-symbolic.svg   (symbolic/apps)

Application icons (app menu entries, mimetype icons, etc.) referenced at
runtime via GAppInfo resolve through the system icon theme (Adwaita) and are
not bundled with this project.
